Villeger et al (2008): NEW MULTIDIMENSIONAL FUNCTIONAL DIVERSITY INDICES
FOR A MULTIFACETED FRAMEWORK IN FUNCTIONAL ECOLOGY. - Ecology, 89(8), 
2008, pp. 2290?2301


